OL,5,G1900 Ramsay's 24 Hours to Hell and Back
OL,6,     FGordon Ramsay visits Bayou on the
OL,7,     FVine, a family-run Cajun
OL,8,     Frestaurant in Kansas City,
OL,9,     FMissouri, where he redecorates
OL,10,     Fwith a jazz theme and revamps the
OL,11,     Fmenu.
OL,12,G2000 Taskmaster Bleeped - The Final
OL,13,     FAmy Gledhill tears her hair out,
OL,14,     FJoel Dommett sniffs the contents
OL,15,     Fof a vacuum and Kumail Nanjiani
OL,16,     Ftrims a cat. Once the dust, lint
OL,17,     Fand fur have settled, our champion
OL,18,     Fis crowned.
